1.Share: should we take care of the weak, the dying and children even though we are in a difficult situation?<br />
<br />
2.Religion: is religion peace? Why are there so many holy wars in the history of mankind?<br />
<br />
3.War: what is the meaning of war? Why do people wage wars?<br />
<br />
4.Refugee camp: how to solve the refugee crisis?<br />
<br />
5.Equality: are people created equal, free and dignified?<br />
<br />
6.What can we do to make the world better?<br />
